    "body": "The requires(compiler, when) directive allows a package to require\r\na specific compiler. This is an usability improvement vs the current\r\nsituation where all non supported compilers have to be listed in\r\nseparate 'conflicts' directive (that also have to be maintained\r\nwhen spack supports new compilers)",
    "performed_via_github_app": null
